ActConvention for the Conservation of Salmon in the North Atlantic Ocean
PrecisAppointment of DAVID DUNN of Shediac, New Brunswick, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of two years, as a Canadian representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization.
